# Two Pointers

This folder contains notes and Python solutions related to the Two Pointer technique.

## Topics Covered

- Fast & Slow Pointers
- Opposite Direction Pointers

## Problems Solved

- Remove Element (LeetCode 27)
- Move Zeroes (LeetCode 283)
- Merge Sorted Array (LeetCode 88)
- Squares of a Sorted Array (LeetCode 977)

## Goal

Learn when and how to apply the Two Pointer technique to solve array problems efficiently.
